snippet.title: Regina & Mac World (Nintendo Switch) Trailer
snippet.description:
Regina and Mac are back in an all new, 2D adventure. On a quest to help their new friend Macbat (from Macbat 64) to find the purpose in his life, the dinosaur and the parrot jump, run, slide and dash through 100 levels filled with secrets. Regina & Mac World will release in June for Switch and in H2 2021 for Wii U (Wii U version only in Europe and Australia).


Music by Badub, game by Diplodocus Games, Macbat is a property of Siactro.
